[
    {
        "content": "<p>we originally settled on the <code>_</code> suffix for names that are reassignable with <code>var</code>, but that was before static dispatch, and the <code>_</code> suffix looks really unfortunate with static dispatch: <span aria-label=\"sweat smile\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f605\" role=\"img\" title=\"sweat smile\">:sweat_smile:</span> </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Ruby\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">iter_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">iter_</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">next</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 547165762,
        "sender_full_name": "Richard Feldman",
        "timestamp": 1761519332
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>it looks fine with the runner-up, which was a <code>$</code> prefix:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Ruby\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"vg\">$iter</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"vg\">$iter</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">next</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 547165789,
        "sender_full_name": "Richard Feldman",
        "timestamp": 1761519363
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>seems like we should go back to that instead - what do others think?</p>",
        "id": 547165813,
        "sender_full_name": "Richard Feldman",
        "timestamp": 1761519387
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I think <code>$</code> looks better in general.</p>",
        "id": 547166683,
        "sender_full_name": "Brendan Hansknecht",
        "timestamp": 1761520363
    }
]